== Usage ==
This template is intended for [[List of cities and municipalities of the Philippines|Philippine cities and municipalities]]. It uses both the [[d:Property:P988|PSGC code]] and [[d:Property:P1082|population]] (including its [[d:Property:P585|point in time]] qualifier) stored in Wikidata. The template returns the population figures for the specified census year, and is primarily intended for use inside <code>{{[[Template:Philippine Census|Philippine Census]]}}</code> tables.

* To retrieve the population by census year, use:
<pre>
{{Philippine census population|1980}}
</pre>

