* To add the current census population, use:
<code><nowiki>
{{Philippine census population|current}}
</nowiki></code>
or
<code><nowiki>
{{Philippine census population}}
</nowiki></code>

==Notes==
The template can also be used on province and region articles, but since many of those articles only store the 2015 population data, the template will give blank results for older censuses which are missing in Wikidata.

